divs: sighting detailsthis may not be a saucer siting as per say, but it is a unusual siting for me. i was walking home from a neighbors house when i saw a string of lights in the sky. there were five lights that i could see. they moved like they were on a string and independent of each other, i have never seen anything like this. they were very bright, a bit brighter than the stars that were out this night. when i got home, i asked my son if he wanted to see a ufo. after checking it out for a minute or two, he called another neighbor of mine, an they came outside to see this strange event. we watched them for awhile, than they started to fade out, kind of like they were getting higher in the atmosphere, then we lost site of them. i saw them for about half an hour or so. this occurred at about 10 pm on 9\1\10, appleton, wi. sorry no photos or vids.
